          </a>
          <noscript>
            <a href="https://fightfascism.glitch.me/">
              <img width="140" height="140" class="lazy-load" title="Fight Fascism sticker by Angus Johnston" alt="Fight fascism" src="https://cdn.glitch.com/4e796d0c-e4ff-46fc-a546-de1ccc1e8663%2Ffight-fascism.png">
            </a>
          </noscript>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 pt-5 mx-auto text-center">
        <p>
          <a href="https://blacklivesmatter.com/">
            <img width="140" height="140" class="lazy-load" alt="Black Lives Matter" title="Black Lives Matter logo" data-src="https://cdn.glitch.com/4e796d0c-e4ff-46fc-a546-de1ccc1e8663%2Fblm.png">
          </a>
          <noscript>
            <a href="https://blacklivesmatter.com/">
